  <name>Shenko</name>
  <summary>Panda3D game engine framework with Blender 3D integration</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Shenko is an open-source platform built on the Panda3D game engine, designed to integrate 
      Panda3D and Blender 3D for Python game development. It provides a menu-driven framework 
      that makes it easy to create games and 3D applications.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Built on Panda3D game engine (1.10.10+)</li>
      <li>Seamless Blender 3D integration</li>
      <li>Menu-driven development framework</li>
      <li>Python-based for easy scripting</li>
      <li>Asset management utilities</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
